src/parallel/ll-dgr-src/poststream_f.f File Reference

Detailed Description

Post-Stream step for order parameter distribution function f in the parallel dual grid D2Q9 Lee-Lin multiphase LBM.

All differential terms are calculated using a second order centered differencing scheme.
